  "body": "**Remixd is crashing when IDE tries to connect to localhost.**\r\n\r\nBehavior:\r\n1. Run `npx remixd` in the folder you want to share.\r\n2. Connect from the remix IDE to localhost (from https://remix.ethereum.org)\r\n3.  In your local computer's terminal, I've got the following WARN `[WARN] You may now only use IDE at https://remix.ethereum.org to connect to that instance\r\n4. It causes `remixd` to crash on your pc\r\n5. Remix IDE gets disconnected (attached image).\r\n\r\nRemixd version: `0.6.9` \r\nOS: `MacOs Monterey 12.1`\r\n\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2022-12-31 at 13 06 28](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16150627/210134496-bc38882a-e5b8-43b7-9dfc-0db763352950.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
